31#define __GMP_FORCE_mpq_neg 1
32
33#include "gmp.h"
34#include "gmp-impl.h"
35
36
37void
38mpq_neg (mpq_ptr dst, mpq_srcptr src)
39{
40 mp_size_t num_size = SIZ(NUM(src));
41
42 if (src != dst)
43 {
44 mp_size_t size;
45 mp_ptr dp;
46
47 size = ABS(num_size);
48 dp = MPZ_NEWALLOC (NUM(dst), size);
49 MPN_COPY (dp, PTR(NUM(src)), size);
50
51 size = SIZ(DEN(src));
52 dp = MPZ_NEWALLOC (DEN(dst), size);
53 SIZ(DEN(dst)) = size;
54 MPN_COPY (dp, PTR(DEN(src)), size);
55 }
56
57 SIZ(NUM(dst)) = -num_size;
58}
